### 测试 A：提交空数据（触发 400 校验错误）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/account/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "toAccount": "",
    "amount": 0
}

###

### 测试 B：提交正常数据（或触发 403 业务逻辑限制）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/account/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "toAccount": "DE12345678",
    "amount": 20000
}